:name:
Hunting

:pool: 
Vigor

:p: 
V

:coretxt:
Vampires naturally able to hunt their pray, humans.
Hunting can be used to chase down the victim as well as to gain trust.
This is typically animalistic form of hunting but it can be used to abuse psychological weak points of mortals.
For example, one could seduce victim, and lead them to some secluse place.

:tags:
Vampiric

